1
00:00:37,559 --> 00:00:43,351
Hey, why do you look so miserable these days?
Did you get your heart broken or something?

2
00:00:51,640 --> 00:00:59,314
Ah, so it is true.
Why? Did that older woman turn you down? Did she say she doesn’t like you?

3
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:03,983
Honestly, I’ve never seen anyone as devoted as you.

4
00:01:03,983 --> 00:01:08,821
Just try seeing someone else.
It might change how you feel.

5
00:01:21,272 --> 00:01:24,354
What a waste of a handsome face, seriously.

6
00:02:56,499 --> 00:02:58,086
What’s wrong?

7
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:03,708
You go ahead.
I’ll go separately.

8
00:03:03,708 --> 00:03:05,959
What? Hey!

9
00:03:49,110 --> 00:03:52,501
Yujin, I’m in front of your place. I’ll wait.

10
00:04:10,209 --> 00:04:12,480
Yujin, I’m in front of your place. I’ll wait.

11
00:04:24,948 --> 00:04:26,288
Hyung...

12
00:04:28,182 --> 00:04:29,825
Please...

13
00:06:28,316 --> 00:06:30,451
Yujin, I’m in front of your place. I’ll wait.

14
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:50,703
That’s strange. Why isn’t he answering?

15
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:57,421
About Taeyoon...
I don’t think he’s even gone to work yet.

16
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:03,875
He should’ve already left for the café by this time.

17
00:07:19,509 --> 00:07:21,089
What’s wrong?

18
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,725
I’m going out for a bit.

19
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:53,011
Pick up...
Please pick up.

20
00:08:35,479 --> 00:08:36,586
Hyung...?

21
00:08:44,339 --> 00:08:45,391
Hyung...?

22
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:54,711
Hyung!

23
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,090
Hyung, look at me.

24
00:09:02,356 --> 00:09:03,589
Hyung!

25
00:09:05,650 --> 00:09:08,782
Hello, someone has collapsed here. He’s unconscious.

26
00:09:08,782 --> 00:09:10,990
Please come quickly. The address is...

27
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:17,147
Hyung, please...

28
00:09:18,959 --> 00:09:20,860
Open your eyes.

29
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,208
Hyung...

30
00:09:31,091 --> 00:09:32,416
I’m here.

31
00:09:33,325 --> 00:09:34,183
Hyung.

32
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,283
Fortunately, it’s nothing serious.

33
00:10:13,283 --> 00:10:17,158
It seems he hasn’t been getting enough sleep lately,
and his body was extremely exhausted.

34
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:23,862
It also seems to have overlapped a bit
with the effects of the medication he was already taking.

35
00:10:23,862 --> 00:10:26,260
He should be fine after getting some more rest.

36
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,221
Yujin.

37
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,978
You’re awake?

38
00:11:10,077 --> 00:11:11,459
Are you okay?

39
00:11:14,583 --> 00:11:16,171
You were scared, weren’t you?

40
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:20,174
I’m sorry.

41
00:11:20,922 --> 00:11:22,834
You must’ve been really frightened.

42
00:11:23,717 --> 00:11:25,247
I’m sorry.

43
00:11:27,639 --> 00:11:29,038
This happened because of me.

44
00:11:30,250 --> 00:11:36,451
No, why would this be because of you?
This is my fault.

45
00:11:38,697 --> 00:11:43,402
Making you worry over me like this...
It’s a little embarrassing.

46
00:12:20,880 --> 00:12:22,153
Yujin.

47
00:12:22,910 --> 00:12:24,959
I have something to say.

48
00:12:27,363 --> 00:12:28,501
Do you really...

49
00:12:29,839 --> 00:12:31,442
have to say it now?

50
00:12:37,366 --> 00:12:40,297
Like an idiot, I only realized it now.

51
00:12:41,079 --> 00:12:43,481
Why I was so shaken.

52
00:12:45,830 --> 00:12:48,451
Why I couldn’t let you go.

53
00:12:54,917 --> 00:12:56,592
For so long...

54
00:12:59,059 --> 00:13:01,676
I’m sorry for making you carry those feelings alone for so long.

55
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:04,621
Hyung...

56
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,372
Yujin.

57
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:23,640
Seeing you cry,

58
00:13:24,422 --> 00:13:26,957
my heart hurt so much.

59
00:14:03,639 --> 00:14:05,276
At last...

60
00:14:08,160 --> 00:14:11,206
your heart finally reached him, Yujin.
